Class CriticalSectionSet

WorkLoadSet.CriticalSectionSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<CriticalSection>, Collection<CriticalSection>, List<CriticalSection>, RandomAccess, SequencedCollection<CriticalSection>
public class CriticalSectionSet extends Vector<CriticalSection>
Container of critical sections belonging to tasks within a workload.

Extends Vector to hold CriticalSection instances. Currently acts as a simple typed collection; additional behaviors (search, aggregation, nesting analysis) can be layered later if needed.
